net/sched: act_tunnel_key: fix OOB write in case of IPv6 ERSPAN tunnels

the following command

 # tc action add action tunnel_key \
 > set src_ip 2001:db8::1 dst_ip 2001:db8::2 id 10 erspan_opts 1:6789:0:0

